author: donaldp
msg: Removed BlockDag/Traversal combo infavour of DependencyGraph.
Also converted DependencyGraph to use static methods and to take a boolean indicating either forward/reverse traversal rather than Traversal object.

author: donaldp
msg: No need to setup BlockDAG as it implements no lifecycle stages.

author: donaldp
msg: Refactored BlockDag so that it no longer requires Container but insteads off an array of BlockMetaData objects passed in.

author: donaldp
msg: Remove PhaseEntry abstraction and directly manipulated objects.
The original reason for abstraction was because it was thought that there may be an unbound number of phases. This did not prove to be true.
